<span id="freeTextContainer14170431778374601757">Excellent, engaging, inspiring, and incredibly interesting. I am usually not a fan of military history, but Fischer&apos;s use of backstory at the perfect moments really drew me in. His scholarship and writing style will have me going on to read other books by him.</span>
  <span id="freeText14170431778374601757" style="display:none">Excellent, engaging, inspiring, and incredibly interesting. I am usually not a fan of military history, but Fischer's use of backstory at the perfect moments really drew me in. His scholarship and writing style will have me going on to read other books by him.</span>
