<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6889967-the-last-founding-father"><img alt="The Last Founding Father: James Monroe and a Nation&#39;s Call to Greatness" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1328847326l/6889967._SX98_.jpg" />
