<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/43177.Brown_V_Board_of_Education"><img alt="Brown V. Board of Education: A Civil Rights Milestone and Its Troubled Legacy" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348516661l/43177._SY75_.jpg" />
