<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/671374.The_Scratch_of_a_Pen"><img alt="The Scratch of a Pen: 1763 and the Transformation of North America" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1433942060l/671374._SY75_.jpg" />
